438\u0442\u0441\u044f \u0441\u0432\u0435\u0442, \u0438 \u0432\u044b \u0431\u0443\u0434\u0435\u0442\u0435 \u0441\u043e\u0431\u0438\u0440\u0430\u0442\u044c \u0441\u043b\u0435\u0434\u0443\u044e\u0449\u0438\u0439 \u043f\u0443\u0442\u044c \u043f\u0440\u0438 \u0441\u0432\u0435\u0442\u0435 \u043c\u0430\u043b\u0435\u043d\u044c\u043a\u043e\u0433\u043e \u0444\u043e\u043d\u0430\u0440\u0438\u043a\u0430, \u043b\u0438\u0431\u043e \u0436\u0435 \u0432\u044b \u043d\u0430\u0443\u0447\u0438\u0442\u0435\u0441\u044c \u043b\u0435\u0442\u0430\u0442\u044c \u0438 \u0441\u043c\u043e\u0436\u0435\u0442\u0435 \u043d\u0430\u0436\u0430\u0442\u044c \u043d\u0430 \u043a\u043d\u043e\u043f\u043a\u0443 \u0431\u0435\u0437 \u043f\u043e\u0441\u0442\u0440\u043e\u0435\u043d\u0438\u044f \u043f\u0443\u0442\u0438\u2026 \u00a0\u0412\u044b\u0431\u0438\u0440\u0430\u0439\u0442\u0435 \u043d\u0430 \u0441\u0432\u043e\u0439 \u0441\u0442\u0440\u0430\u0445 \u0438 \u0440\u0438\u0441\u043a. \u0423\u0434\u0430\u0447\u0438!</p>\n<p>===========================================================</p>\n<p>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Welcome to the \u201cMake your choice\u201d!\r\n  </p>\n<p>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 You are small, but very tenacious toy, that wants to escape from strange huge room. To do this you should complete several levels and in every level it is necessary to just choose one of the buttons(blue or red) and press on it. But be carefully! Every your decision will affect you in the future, helping or conversely preventing next level\u2019s passing.</p>\n<p>Rules.\r\n  </p>\n<p>\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Every level has 2 buttons \u2013 blue and red. To complete level it is necessary to reach one of the buttons, using \u201clego\u201d blocks, and press on it. Who should you do it?\r\n  </p>\n<ul><li>To move character use \u201cW\u201d, \u201cA\u201d, \u201cS\u201d, \u201cD\u201d or arrows;\r\n  </li><li>To watch on sides move mouse;\r\n  </li><li>To jump press space;\r\n  </li><li>To take \u201clego\u201d block approach it(you will see contour of the block) and press \u201cE\u201d;\r\n  </li><li>To throw block on random place press left mouse button(LBM);\r\n  </li><li>Transfer block to your path and come to place where you want to put block. Game shows you variants of placement. Choose necessary one and press left button on mouse(LBM);\r\n  </li><li>To rotate block while during placement use mouse wheel;\r\n  </li><li>Path must start from white block. It\u2019s already waiting for you on every level;\r\n  </li><li>On every block it is possible to put just one block.</li></ul>\n<p>One of the buttons always seems more attractive and available than another, but be careful, because every of them has positive or negative affect on next level. Who knows, maybe electricity will turn off and you will build next path with just small lamp or you will be able to fly and you will can press every button without any blocks\u2026 Choose at your own risk. Good luck!</p>", "metacritic": null, "released": "2021-04-12", "tba": false, "updated": "2021-04-12T15:20:47", "background_image": "https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/5b2/5b22d3f967371902a5b105fff52b2fdc.jpg", "website": "", "rating": 0.0, "rating_top": 0, "added_by_status": null, "playtime": 0, "achievements_count": 0, "ratings_count": 0, "suggestions_count": 36, "game_series_count": 0, "reviews_count": 0, "platforms": ["PC"], "developers": ["vika98z"], "genres": [], "publishers": [], "esrb_rating": null}